Find in Project (Gedit Plugin)
Andrew Liu <andrewliu33 (at) gmail com>

Version 1.2.0
Github location: http://github.com/eggegg/find-in-project

Features:
* Search files within project with ack-grep or grep
* Good gui look
* Context for matched lines
* Support regular expression

Dependencies:
* filebrowser plugin enabled
* python-webkitgtk
* ack-grep (optional, fallback to grep if it doesn't exist)

This is a AckMate clone version for Gedit.
<Ctrl><Shift><f> to open the search window.
Click on the search result to open the files with certain line numbers.

